snippet.title: Welcome to JumpStart!
snippet.description:
JumpStart is an online virtual world that's designed to make learning fun for kids. Join us today to take on a series of amazing adventures. Along the way you will even be able to customize your very own Jumpee and game!

Learn more about JumpStart's

Online games: 
http://www.jumpstart.com/parents/games/online-games

http://www.jumpstart.com/parents/games/learning-games
